{"tid":950957,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港航危機】擔心香港航空破產？兩款本地旅遊保險連航空公司倒閉都照保","createTime":"2018-12-22T02:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T01:37:20.000Z","uid":51464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bf2ece01d33903b4e598a29235b3f2f4b7672d78","tid":950957,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:54:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2236418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2236418&d=l9aZWPgK1g3ajVNLadFgEYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=1a4d7ab3\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2236418</a><br />\n<br />\n香港航空的債券淪為垃圾債券，加上公司高層「跳船」，令人擔心香港航空隨時破產，已預訂機票的乘客隨時因航空公司倒閉而未能出發。雖然香港航空已發出聲明，表明會繼續「如常營運」，但為了安全起見，建議已購買香港航空相關機票的乘客，最好購買為航空公司結業提供保障的旅遊保險服務！<br />\n<br />\n絕大部分保險公司所提供的旅遊保險，雖然提供「取消旅程」的相關保障，但一般只適用於因受保人／其直系親屬／旅遊夥伴／密切商業夥伴身故、嚴重受傷或嚴重疾病；受保人須出庭作證、強制隔離或當陪審團；目的地突然爆發罷工、暴動、民亂、惡劣天氣、傳染病；受保人住所因火災或水淹導致嚴重損毀等原因，受保人才可獲得保障。如因航空公司破產，引致航班取消的話，則不屬於「取消旅程」的保障範圍。<br />\n<br />\n藍十字‧中銀航空公司執笠都照保！<br />\n==========================================<br />\n買保險要睇清條款！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e6e0f98c02cb7f5eee0b7528085df040876588","tid":950957,"uid":86383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dd3bfd0cf081c32ebda3175818f8602fb6d5e4","tid":950957,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T17:44: